title: Wine & Webinar
desc: Join SWE-OC for wine tasting and networking followed by a recorded SWE webinar and group discussion. We will be viewing the webinar on the topic of "Invisibility Only Works for Superheros! Helping Others to Notice and Value Your Contributions." There are three factors that are critical to success: performance, image, and exposure. This webinar will show you how to strengthen your performance, define your image, and get more exposure so that you can be seen in the professional world. Please bring your favorite bottle of wine (or beverage of choice) to share with? fellow SWE-OC members! Snacks will also be provided.
